## 5. SYSTEM TESTING

### Types of Testing
- **Unit Testing**: Testing individual NLP functions (`extract_location`) for accuracy.
- **Integration Testing**: Ensuring the Chat Interface correctly communicates with the Django Backend.
- **User Acceptance Testing (UAT)**: Verifying that responses are helpful and formatted correctly for the end-user.

### Example Test Cases
| Input | Expected Output | Status |
|---|---|---|
| "Hello" | Greeting from Bot + "How can I help you today?" | Pass |
| "What do people eat in Italy?" | Displays "Traditional Food" and "Eating Style" for Italy. | Pass |
| "Wedding dress in India" | Shows details for Saree/Lehenga and Sherwani. | Pass |
| "Tell me about Mars" | Locations not found -> Fallback to general info or error message. | Pass |

